data.title: Petrol And Oil Mini Gas Pump Globes
data.meta_description: National Bezole Mixture Globe. Petrol And Oil Mini Gas Pump Globes. Hand blown milk white opaline mini reproduction glass mini gas pump globe
data.text:
CLICK HERE FOR LED LAMP BASE OPTIONS

Hand blown milk white opaline reproduction glass gas pump globe with decals applied to both front and reverse faces

Decals on the 8" Mini and 10" Large are water slide transfers printed at high quality then finished by treating with heat for durability. Suitable for indoor use. Scratch resistant, waterproof and quite hardy. We do not recommend prolonged exposure to UV light

NOTE: this listing is for the globe only, our LED lamp base options can be found here

Look great in garages, display cases, shelves, offices, and are an ideal gift for those petrol head and vintage memorabilia addicts! Treat Dad to a fantastic birthday present.

Condition is brand new, and made up on receipt of order.

Height Round 8" Mini Globe only 8 1/2 inches / 22cm / 220mm neck diameter 3 1/8 inches / 8cm / 80mm Round 10" Large Globe only 10 1/2 inches / 26cm / 260mm neck diameter 3 1/8 inches / 8cm / 80mm

Please note: all dimensions are approximate and can vary slightly as these are hand made products
